Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used the Tetsusaiga to\nbreak through Naraku's barrier{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I almost had him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he abandoned his castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he disappeared leaving\nno trace at all... not even his scent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku had completely\ndisappeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon Naraku had\nleft behind in his castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}told us that Naraku had gone to\na place "where no one could touch him."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there really such a place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was probably so confident\nthat he wouldn't be found{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that he allowed the demon\nto say such a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll devour you,\NSacred Jewel shards and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:13.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just huge, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:31.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we can't stay idle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, I'll find Naraku\nand destroy him forgood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!\NWhere, Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, I sensed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demonic aura's been getting\nstronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Appear, apparition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will die,\nweasel-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be wandering about\nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on home and\nsleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anotherdemon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this how you repay\na debt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't even try to\nstop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, hold him still!\NHold him still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon dispersal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons are increasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thatexplains the demonic\naura in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demonic aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We journey around the countryside\nslaying demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we're in the same business...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, due to this sudden\nincrease in demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had to come out of retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just an old woman's whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better you stay retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I teach you a\nlesson again, dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now... Madam Exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you know the reason\nforthe increase in demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of the Demon's Head Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon's Head Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It probably has a proper name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buteveryone calls it\NDemon's Head Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's said that the head of a demon\nvanquished by an ancestor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was buried to ward off evil spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the castle was built overit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd believe stories\nthat you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But for some strange reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,lately, the demon has been revived,\ntormenting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And no amount of exorcism\nhas worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To Demon's Head Castle.\NWhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you travel\naround slaying demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no time\nforthis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But since we know\nthe story...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finding Naraku is\ntop priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand the reward\nis great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now... let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We split the earnings evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did not see anything!\NNothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, our lord has been\nacting strange in recent days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He locks himself up in his room\nand refuses to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't the castle sorta creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, that field was nothing\ncompared to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this must be the core\nof the demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From the severed demon's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has surrounded the\nentire castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy the glum look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what're you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all sense the demonic aura\nand are uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demonic aura?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... don't you feel or\nsense anything weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Like what", you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all in your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or are you all feeling scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still young, yet so hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think this old woman\nis a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Even I sense\nthe demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the seventh one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The lord slays every vassal ormaid\nthat tries to approach his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you think the lord's erratic\nbehavioris caused by the demon curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon appears afterdark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until then, stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One... two... three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One... two... three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now listen up.\NYou must be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so full of energy, old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll say. She's amazing\namidst this demonic aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even forthose as well-trained as us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the demonic aura in this castle\nis unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's finish up this job\nand get out of here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are the ones who've come\nto exterminate the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And please save my father\nwithout fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are the princess\nof this castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Many priests and priestesses\nhave failed at exorcising the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest assured, my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:45.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall stand firm here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and conduct the exorcism\nno matter how many days it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you say we should finish this\nup quickly and leave?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not worry.\NLeave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go! Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll destroy it in one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango seems so intense today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It went right through!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happening?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hit it square with my\NWind Scar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it didn't even flinch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That demon's head... could it be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:44.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:45.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If my Wind Scar didn't work,\nhow do you expect to destroy it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No weapon will work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spiritual Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess, the demon's head...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean the demon head will\nappear again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. That is just make-believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An illusion to divert attention\nfrom the real demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:52.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means the real demon is hiding\nsomewhere in this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demonic aura hasn't subsided at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... demonic aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some exorcist you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that the lord\nis deranged?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ratherthan a demon's curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you sure the lord isn't possessed\nby the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are noticed,\nyou will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When that time comes,\NI'lljust fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He {\i1}is{\i0} the lord of the castle,\nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... he's definitely human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe that the demonic\naura covering this castle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is coming from the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, don't you feel a\nlittle better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Not any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did it work on you, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a very special\npurification salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most demons succumb\nto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! What a fake exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if it'd work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'll test it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Overhere, overhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon disperse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father could be the demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to the monk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yourfatheris just possessed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the demon himself\ncould be elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The princess would like\nto see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't intend to\ngo alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's true the princess\nis very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Who'd worry about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't know when the\ndemon will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to\ngo alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's what you mean,\ndon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is quite strong\nby himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why the glare?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still have much to learn about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! You fake exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about her\nability as an exorcist,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but she's pretty sharp\nas a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:29.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this purification salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take one packet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a very long stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You probably have heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The burial site of the\ndemon head is down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon head burial site?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beneath this castle is buried,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the head of a vanquished demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:12.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would like you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that to ward off evil,\nthe demon's head was buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until now, there was never\na problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:26.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The burial site was uncovered\nand the demon escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And inside this hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}T- This is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the skeletons of\nthe priests and priestesses
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who tried to exterminate\nthe demon and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:22.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon of this castle craved\nhumans like them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and absorbed theirpowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why it wants me here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To absorb your spiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, that Miroku is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... he's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're talking about that lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By now, he's with the\nprincess and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, noteven Miroku would do\nanything in this demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! He's so lecherous, a\ndemonic aura wouldn't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, probably he's feeling\nquite comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have no sense\nof delicacy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Notenough training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Sango, maybe we should\ngo and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:29.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not necessary.\NI don't want to interrupt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's forcing herself to say that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The lord is... turning into a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-The lord... the lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he's the demon after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The airin here is\nfilled with demonic aura
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and your body\nshould be going numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:07.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I added my own spiritual power\nto the exorcist's purification salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems to have some effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is bad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This demon is quite powerful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And my body won't move\ndue to the demonic aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, there's no help\nforthcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, that half-demon is\nprobably fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the lord back at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I used my magic to manipulate\nthat puppet lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:51.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hope you're prepared, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll finish you in one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku hasn't come back since
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he went underground\nwith the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Sango is still so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:55.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and I are the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,able to set up a preview\nforthe next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}not{\i0} the time\nto be sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:08.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... the princess is sleeping\nso comfortably, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Secret of the Possessed Princess"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.46,0:24:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on anyway?!
